          "datePublished": "2022-04-01",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Mixed Feelings...\nDefinitely one of the better schools on the area. Current admin and staffs are good. Specially Principal, Dr. Shivashankari Ma'am, is very helpful and caring. Management need to work on few aspects specially on timing of the school, which is very tiring and exhausting. I wish they can reduce some amount of school timing. Students also get exhausted a lot at the end of the day, and the second most important thing is the criteria for the selection of staff if you have B.Ed and 3 more years of experience. Then maybe salary will be a issue. Teachers are helpful and do best for the students. One extra star for the student who are really good and priceless.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
