            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best school in this selaiyur area. It takes an education to the next level. run by a professional who is having more than 30 years of experience in education field. Good supportive staffs to mold our children.\n\n🌟 Technically sounds good.👍\n🌟 Situated in the inner street area.👎\n🌟 Please take care of your children while drop/pickup...due to narrow street....\n🌟 School timings can be considered.\n🌟 App is there but it should be updated to give more details of the students like attendance, marks....",
